        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Zest <strong>half</strong> your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lemon[s] </strong>(try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p><p>Add the <strong>browned</strong> <strong>rosemary chicken</strong> to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined tray (reserve the pan!) with your <strong>dried oregano</strong>, <strong>dried basil</strong>, <strong>lemon zest</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a grind of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 12-15 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1653317816713-x200.jpg",
