    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>smoked streaky bacon</strong> and cook for 2-3 min on each side or until golden and crisp then transfer to kitchen paper – this is your<strong> crispy bacon</strong></p>",
