    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Separate 1 outer leaf per person from the<strong> lettuce</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lettuce</strong> into quarters, lengthways</p><p>Put your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in the oven for 5 min or until it's warm and crusty, then carefully slice in half before serving</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
