    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, transfer it to a clean board and pull it apart, using two forks – this technique is known as 'pulling'</p><p>Return the <strong>pulled chicken</strong> to the pan along with the juice of the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>Caesar chicken</strong></p>",
