    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build, fill the <strong>warmed ciabatta</strong> with some <strong>Caesar dressing</strong>, <strong>Caesar chicken</strong>,<strong> crispy bacon</strong>, <strong>sliced tomato </strong>and an <strong>outer lettuce leaf </strong>– this is your <strong>chicken & bacon Caesar sandwich</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>lettuce quarters</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>Caesar dressing</strong> and sprinkle over the <strong>remaining grated Italian cheese</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>rosemary fries</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
